title: Steelers, Lakers, Aaron Rodgers, and the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Steelers, Lakers, Aaron Rodgers, and the Blazing 5
description:
Colin discusses the dominance of the Pittsburgh Steelers last night, why we shouldn't count out the Los Angeles Lakers, an interesting stat about Green Bay Packers QB Aaron Rodgers, and his Blazing 5 picks for this weekend. Guests include DeAngleo Hall, Rob Parker, Kevin Clark, Eric Dickerson, and Jason McIntyre.
